statements: SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data ORDER BY trade_time DESC;
SELECT trade_price, trade_quantity FROM trade_execution_data WHERE stock_symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT AVG(trade_price) AS average_price FROM trade_execution_data;
SELECT trade_id, trade_time, algorithm_confidence FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_price > 100 ORDER BY trade_time ASC;
SELECT stock_symbol, trade_quantity FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_quantity < 1000;
SELECT trade_id, trade_time, stock_symbol, trade_price, trade_quantity, algorithm_confidence FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_price > 100 ORDER BY trade_time DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data WHERE stock_symbol IN ('AAPL', 'GOOGL', 'MSFT') AND trade_quantity > 1000 ORDER BY trade_time ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT trade_time, stock_symbol, trade_price FROM trade_execution_data WHERE algorithm_confidence > 0.8 ORDER BY trade_time DESC
SELECT trade_id, trade_price, algorithm_confidence FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_quantity = 500 AND trade_price < 50 ORDER BY trade_time ASC
SELECT trade_id, trade_time, stock_symbol, trade_quantity FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY trade_time DESC LIMIT 3
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data;
SELECT stock_symbol, trade_price, trade_qty FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_price > 1000;
SELECT trade_id, trade_price, trade_qty, executed_by FROM trade_execution_data ORDER BY trade_price DESC;
SELECT trade_id, stock_symbol, trade_timestamp, trade_price, trade_qty, executed_by FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_qty > 100 ORDER BY trade_timestamp ASC;
SELECT analysis_id, trade_id, accuracy, profit_loss FROM neural_network_analysis WHERE accuracy >= 0.9 ORDER BY analysis_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data ORDER BY trade_timestamp DESC, trade_price ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT trade_id, stock_symbol, trade_price FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_price > 1000;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data WHERE executed_by LIKE '%John%' AND trade_qty > 100 ORDER BY trade_timestamp DESC;

SELECT trade_id, stock_symbol, trade_qty, trade_price * trade_qty AS total_trade_value FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-12-31 23:59:59' ORDER BY trade_price DESC;

SELECT t.trade_id, t.stock_symbol, n.accuracy, n.profit_loss FROM trade_execution_data t JOIN neural_network_analysis n ON t.trade_id = n.trade_id WHERE n.accuracy > 80 AND n.profit_loss > 0 ORDER BY n.analysis_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM trades ORDER BY trade_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_price, trade_quantity FROM trades WHERE trade_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT trade_id, log_timestamp, log_message FROM trade_logs ORDER BY log_timestamp ASC, log_id DESC;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_price FROM trades WHERE trade_price > 100 ORDER BY trade_price DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT trade_id, profit_loss, trade_accuracy FROM trade_performance WHERE profit_loss < 0.0 ORDER BY trade_accuracy DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_price FROM trades WHERE trade_price > 50 ORDER BY trade_date DESC, trade_quantity ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT trade_symbol, AVG(profit_loss) AS avg_profit_loss FROM trade_performance GROUP BY trade_symbol HAVING avg_profit_loss > 1000 ORDER BY avg_profit_loss DESC;
SELECT * FROM trades JOIN trade_performance ON trades.id = trade_performance.trade_id WHERE trade_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' AND profit_loss < 0 ORDER BY trade_price ASC;
SELECT trade_symbol, COUNT(*) AS trade_count FROM trades GROUP BY trade_symbol HAVING trade_count > 5 ORDER BY trade_count DESC, trade_symbol ASC;

SELECT trade_symbol, trade_price, profit_loss AS PnL FROM trades LEFT JOIN trade_performance ON trades.id = trade_performance.trade_id WHERE trade_symbol LIKE 'AAPL%' AND PnL IS NOT NULL ORDER BY trade_price DESC, PnL ASC;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data;
SELECT trade_id, timestamp, symbol FROM trade_execution_data WHERE quantity > 100;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM trade_execution_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT AVG(price) AS average_price FROM trade_execution_data WHERE symbol='AAPL';
SELECT * FROM neural_network_data WHERE prediction > 0.5 AND confidence > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM trade_execution_data WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT symbol, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM trade_execution_data GROUP BY symbol;
SELECT t.trade_id, t.timestamp, n.prediction, n.confidence FROM trade_execution_data t JOIN neural_network_data n ON t.trade_id = n.trade_id ORDER BY t.trade_id ASC, n.prediction_timestamp DESC;

SELECT p.neural_network_id, p.learning_rate, p.activation_function FROM model_parameters p JOIN neural_network_data n ON p.neural_network_id = n.neural_network_id WHERE n.confidence > 0.8 ORDER BY p.learning_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data ORDER BY trade_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM neural_network_trades WHERE prediction_accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT trade_id, trade_date, symbol, price FROM trade_performance_metrics WHERE win_ratio >= 0.7 AND loss_ratio <= 0.3;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_predictions WHERE prediction_value > actual_value ORDER BY prediction_date ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT prediction_id, symbol, prediction_value, actual_value FROM neural_network_predictions WHERE actual_value < prediction_value ORDER BY prediction_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY price DESC, quantity ASC;
SELECT trade_id, symbol, quantity, price, execution_type FROM trade_execution_data WHERE quantity > 1000 AND execution_type = 'market' ORDER BY trade_date;
SELECT symbol, AVG(price) AS avg_price, COUNT(trade_id) AS trade_count FROM trade_execution_data GROUP BY symbol HAVING AVG(price) > 50;
SELECT trade_id, symbol, price FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-06-30' AND price > (SELECT AVG(price) FROM trade_execution_data);
SELECT trade_id, symbol, quantity, execution_type FROM trade_execution_data WHERE symbol IN ('AAPL', 'GOOG', 'MSFT') ORDER BY trade_date DESC, quantity DESC;
